> **UMAC** is a full-stack analytics platform that benchmarks the military capabilities of 140+ countries using live 2025 defense data. It automates the entire pipeline — from intelligent web scraping and data engineering to KPI-driven analysis. Insights are finally delivered through interactive Power BI dashboards for powerful global comparison and decision support.
